sequenceDiagram
    participant Eng as Engineer
    participant FIS as AWS FIS
    participant Target as Target Resource
    participant CW as CloudWatch
    participant Alert as Alerting

    Eng->>FIS: Start experiment
    FIS->>Target: Inject failure
    Target->>CW: Emit metrics
    CW->>FIS: Check stop conditions
    
    alt Stop condition met
        FIS->>Target: Execute rollback
        FIS->>Alert: Send notification
    else Experiment complete
        FIS->>Eng: Return results
    end
